WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'SafeKraker' is a code-breaking type of game, where you try to
find the secret 3-number combination in the least amount of moves.

  The numbers in each column range from 1 to 7, there is a padlock
icon on top of each column that opens when you have found the
right number for that column.

  SafeKraker features two types of game: 

 -The 'Easy' game, where you change the numbers in each column,
  when you find one of the right numbers, it's corresponding
  padlock will open.

 -The 'Normal' game, where you have to find all the three numbers
  in order for all the padlocks to open. You have around 336
  possible combinations to try!

  Have fun!

